item.title: Thesis
item.description: The thesis project I completed a thesis in Applied Mathematics, entitled “Network inference from incomplete abundance data”. This work was supervised by Stéphane Robin and Christophe Ambroise and realised at the French Mathématiques et Informatique appliquées Lab (MIA-Paris). Manuscript Defense presentation
